Revision history for perl-shared

0.005  2026-04-14
    - Collapsed Evergreen org-unit lookup into Bibliomation::Shared::Evergreen and removed the standalone EvergreenOrgUnits module.
    - Merged org-unit coverage into the Evergreen test suite and updated module load checks.
    - Documented the shared-library design rules that shared modules must not depend on one another and must not perform application logging.

0.004  2026-04-13
    - Removed incorrect MakeMaker PM path overrides so built distributions preserve the Bibliomation::Shared namespace.

0.003  2026-04-13
    - Added Archive and FileIO shared modules for tar.gz creation and text/delimited file output.
    - Added tests for archive creation and file I/O helpers.
    - Updated distribution metadata and README documentation for the new modules.

0.002  2026-04-13
    - Standardized all shared modules under the Bibliomation::Shared namespace.
    - Expanded README documentation for downstream consumers.
    - Added Evergreen, logging, and email behavior tests.
    - Improved Database SQL-file handling and chunked query parameter binding.
    - Added multipart email support and richer logging helpers.
    - Declared DBD::Pg as an explicit runtime dependency.

0.001  2026-04-13
    - Initial scaffold for shared modules.
